38e38edfbce6b5ef27335a67bdb3f_400x224.jpg"><div class="VagueImage-mask is-active"></div></div></div></div><div class="RichContent-inner"><span class="RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText" itemProp="text">（友情提示，如果你是六级580以上玩家，请直接出门左拐交钱考雅思，不用看别人的心得，总分6.5以上）我之所以这么说，是因为之前看到很多答案都是复习几天考了个7.5或8，感觉并不适合广大群众，毕竟有天赋的人是少数，不能给刚入雅思坑的人一种轻轻松松就过的错觉。我自认为不算笨，也还是努力了很久才拿到了自己想要的成绩，我要做的就是把我的复习方法，准确来说是提升英语的方法，分享给大家。原问题是“自学”，我想培训机构…</span><button type="button" class="Button ContentItem-more Button--plain">阅读全文<span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--ArrowDown ContentItem-arrowIcon" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12 13L8.285 9.218a.758.758 0 0 0-1.064 0 .738.738 0 0 0 0 1.052l4.249 4.512a.758.758 0 0 0 1.064 0l4.246-4.512a.738.738 0 0 0 0-1.052.757.757 0 0 0-1.063 0L12.002 13z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></button></div><div class="ContentItem-actions"><span><button aria-label="赞同" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--up"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleUp VoteButton-TriangleUp" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10"><path d="M2 18.242c0-.326.088-.532.237-.896l7.98-13.203C10.572 3.57 11.086 3 12 3c.915 0 1.429.571 1.784 1.143l7.98 13.203c.15.364.236.57.236.896 0 1.386-.875 1.9-1.955 1.9H3.955c-1.08 0-1.955-.517-1.955-1.9z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span>赞同 <!-- -->9.5K</button><button aria-label="反对" type="button" class="Button VoteButton VoteButton--down"><span style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center">​<svg class="Zi Zi--TriangleDown" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="10" height="10"><path d="M20.044 3H3.956C2.876 3 2 3.517 2 4.9c0 .326.087.533.236.896L10.216 19c.355.571.87 1.143 1.784 1.143s1.429-.572 1.784-1.143l7.98-13.204c.149-.363.236-.57.236-.896 0-1.386-.876-1.9-1.956-1.9z" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></span></button></span><button type="button" class="Button ContentItem-action 